  "Description": {
    "English": "Specialist <span class=\"name name-fuel\">high temperature</span> weapon attachment for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Multi-Tool</span>. Access fire mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> and fire weapon with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>.<br><br>The <span class=\"name name-technology\">Incinerator</span> focuses internal lasers onto the naturally-occuring exhaust gases generated by the Multi-Tool. Ignition results in a highly destructive, if short range, inferno.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "适用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">多用途工具</span>的专业型<span class=\"name name-fuel\">高温</span>武器附件。按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>即可进入发射模式，使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>开火。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">焚化者</span>可将内部激光聚焦到多用途工具自然产生的废气上，点火后可在短程内引发极具毁灭性的火海。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">工具組</span>的專業<span class=\"name name-fuel\">高溫</span>武器配件。按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 進入火焰模式後按 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 發射武器。<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">焚化槍</span>能將內部雷射集中打向工具組自然產生的廢氣。點燃後可在近距離範圍內創造極具破壞性的烈火煉獄。"
  },
